## 資料夾對應

```
assets/
├── brick/        → Brick Wall 材質
├── metal/        → Metal Plate 材質
├── rock/         → Rock Surface 材質
└── rusty_metal/  → Rusty Metal 材質
```

Channel 可用性：

| 材質 | Albedo | Normal | Roughness | AO | Metalness | Displacement |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| brick | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | — | ✓ |
| metal | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | — | ✓ | ✓ |
| rock | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | — | ✓ |
| rusty_metal | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | — | ✓ | ✓ |
